<Turn speaker="spk2" startTime="336.061" endTime="347.990" fidelity="high">
<Sync time=" 336.061"/>
Pol petih letih dela v Bohinju je dobil Martin Golob lani spomladi obvestilo o premestitvi v Grosuplje, kar je dvignilo veliko prahu. 
<Sync time=" 346.651"/>
