<Turn speaker="spk2" startTime="357.786" endTime="369.353" fidelity="high">
<Sync time=" 357.786"/>
Martin Golob, 
<Sync time=" 358.892"/>
ostala sva v Srednji vasi v Bohinju. 
<Sync time=" 361.450"/>
